---
layout: base.njk
title: Home
description: "Pediatric therapy clinic in Colorado Springs — ABA therapy, occupational therapy, speech therapy & physical therapy for children. Autism treatment, sensory processing, AAC specialists. Free screenings. Accepting Medicaid & TRICARE."
---

<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="hero" id="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg" style="background-image: url('/images/hero-therapy.jpg');"></div>
  <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <h1>Nurturing Every Child's Potential—Together!</h1>
    <p>We are a multi-disciplinary team in Colorado Springs, offering a full spectrum of pediatric therapy services from infancy through adolescence.</p>
    <a href="{{ settings.screeningUrl }}" class="btn-cta">📋 Schedule Your Free Screening</a>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Core Values Section -->
<section class="section section-light" id="values-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Our Core Values</h2>
      <p>The principles that guide everything we do</p>
    </div>
    <div class="values-grid">
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="value-icon">🤝</div>
        <h3>Integrity</h3>
        <p>Building trust with families through honesty, transparency, and consistent follow-through in all we do.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="value-icon">🌈</div>
        <h3>Inclusion</h3>
        <p>Honoring every child's unique identity and ensuring that all families feel welcomed, valued, and respected.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="value-icon">🌱</div>
        <h3>Adaptability</h3>
        <p>Meeting children where they are, adjusting our approaches as they grow, and evolving with them over time.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="value-icon">👥</div>
        <h3>Collaboration</h3>
        <p>Collaboration across disciplines—and with families—to create truly individualized care plans.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem; max-width: 700px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
      <p>We believe that therapy should not only address developmental challenges but also <strong>empower children to thrive</strong>, and <strong>equip families to feel supported every step of the way</strong>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<!-- Awards Section -->
<section style="padding: 2.5rem 0; background: white;">
  <div class="container" style="text-align: center;">
    <div style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 1.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fdf6e3 0%, #f5e6b8 100%); border: 2px solid #c9a84c; border-radius: 16px; padding: 1.5rem 2.5rem; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(201,168,76,0.2);">
      <img src="/images/partners/BOTS-2025-Logo-blk.png" alt="Best of Colorado Springs 2025" style="height: 80px; width: auto;">
      <div style="text-align: left;">
        <h3 style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.3rem; color: var(--dark-blue);">Best of Colorado Springs</h3>
        <p style="margin: 0; color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.95rem;">Top 3 finalist in <strong>7 categories</strong> — voted by the community</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Wave Divider -->
<div class="wave-divider">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 1200 80" preserveAspectRatio="none">
    <path d="M0,40 C300,0 600,80 900,40 C1050,20 1150,30 1200,40 L1200,0 L0,0 Z" fill="white"/>
  </svg>
</div>

<!-- Services Section -->
<section class="section section-blue" id="services-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Our Services</h2>
      <p>Comprehensive pediatric therapy tailored to your child's needs</p>
    </div>
    <div class="services-grid">
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-card-img" style="background-image: url('/images/service-aba.jpg');"></div>
        <div class="service-card-body">
          <h3>ABA Therapy</h3>
          <p>Personalized, intensive ABA services for children ages 2–12 with autism spectrum disorders. Center-based and home-based options.</p>
          <a href="/aba/" class="btn-learn-more">Learn More →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-card-img" style="background-image: url('/images/service-ot.jpg');"></div>
        <div class="service-card-body">
          <h3>Occupational Therapy</h3>
          <p>Sensory and motor-based approaches improving daily functioning, play skills, and self-care independence.</p>
          <a href="/occupational-therapy/" class="btn-learn-more">Learn More →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-card-img" style="background-image: url('/images/service-pt.jpg');"></div>
        <div class="service-card-body">
          <h3>Physical Therapy</h3>
          <p>Enhancing movement abilities and developmental milestones for children with delays, genetic disorders, and orthopedic conditions.</p>
          <a href="/physical-therapy/" class="btn-learn-more">Learn More →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-card-img" style="background-image: url('/images/service-speech.jpg');"></div>
        <div class="service-card-body">
          <h3>Speech Therapy</h3>
          <p>Addressing speech, language, voice, fluency, and swallowing with expertise in AAC and childhood apraxia.</p>
          <a href="/speech-therapy/" class="btn-learn-more">Learn More →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Google Reviews Section -->
<section class="section" id="testimonials-section" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a3a5c 0%, #2a5a8c 100%);">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 style="color: white;">What Families Are Saying</h2>
      <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);">Real Google reviews from the families we serve</p>
    </div>

    <script src="https://elfsightcdn.com/platform.js" async></script>

    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2rem; max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; transform: scale(0.85); transform-origin: top center;">
      <div>
        <h3 style="color: white; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 1rem;">⭐ Powers Clinic</h3>
        <div class="elfsight-app-60aa8037-a149-42c7-b119-32f483218f35" data-elfsight-app-lazy></div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 style="color: white; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 1rem;">⭐ Academy Clinic</h3>
        <div class="elfsight-app-4b35ac73-92a4-49ce-a30d-c60bbbea1c51" data-elfsight-app-lazy></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Wave Divider -->
<div class="wave-divider flip">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 1200 80" preserveAspectRatio="none">
    <path d="M0,40 C300,80 600,0 900,40 C1050,60 1150,50 1200,40 L1200,80 L0,80 Z" fill="#2a5a8c"/>
  </svg>
</div>

<!-- Locations Section -->
<section class="section" id="locations-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Come Visit Today!</h2>
      <p>Two convenient locations in Colorado Springs</p>
    </div>
    <div class="locations-grid">
      {% for loc in settings.locations %}
      <div class="location-card">
        <h3>📍 {{ loc.name }}</h3>
        <div class="address">{{ loc.address }}, {{ loc.city }}, {{ loc.state }} {{ loc.zip }}</div>
        <div class="phone">📞 <a href="tel:{{ loc.phone | replace('(', '') | replace(')', '') | replace(' ', '') | replace('-', '') }}">{{ loc.phone }}</a></div>
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 0.75rem;">
          <a href="{{ loc.mapUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-directions">🗺️ Get Directions →</a>
          {% if loc.reviewUrl %}
            <a href="{{ loc.reviewUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-directions" style="background: #f5a623; color: white;">⭐ Leave a Review</a>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Insurance & Partners Section -->
<section class="section section-light" id="insurance-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Insurance</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="partners-grid">
      {% for partner in insurance.items %}
        <div class="partner-badge">
          {% if partner.logo %}
            <img src="{{ partner.logo }}" alt="{{ partner.name }}" class="partner-logo">
          {% else %}
            {{ partner.name }}
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>

    <h3 style="text-align: center; margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--dark-blue);">Community Partners</h3>
    <div class="partners-grid" style="justify-content: center;">
      {% for partner in communityPartners.items %}
        <div class="partner-badge" style="min-width: 200px; max-width: 200px;">
          {% if partner.logo %}
            <img src="{{ partner.logo }}" alt="{{ partner.name }}" class="partner-logo" style="height: 80px;">
          {% else %}
            {{ partner.name }}
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
